Explain how Burp Suite allows us to analyze web application traffic.
    Burp Suite allows us to intercept, inspect, and modify the web traffic between our browser and the servers to analyze and test web applications' security.

What does the Repeater tool allow us to do with requests?
    The Repeater tool in Burp Suite enables us to manually modify and resend web requests to test the responses of web applications.

Why might this be a useful tool for an attacker?
    This tool is useful for attackers because it allows them to manipulate requests to discover vulnerabilities, such as input validation flaws or security misconfigurations, in web applications.



